"diṭṭheva dhamme aññaṃ ārādheyya, evaṃ sampadamidaṃ, sāriputta, vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn12:28.5"
msgid ""
"Taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā "
"yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:29.1"
msgid "Aṭṭha kho imā, sāriputta, parisā."
msgstr "Sāriputta, there are these eight assemblies."

msgctxt "mn12:29.2"
msgid "Katamā aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "mn12:29.3"
msgid ""
"Khattiyaparisā, brāhmaṇaparisā, gahapatiparisā, samaṇaparisā, "
"cātumahārājikaparisā, tāvatiṃsaparisā, māraparisā, brahmaparisā—"
msgstr ""
"The assemblies of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, and ascetics. An "
"assembly of the gods under the Four Great Kings. An assembly of the gods "
"under the Thirty-Three. An assembly of Māras. An assembly of Brahmās."

msgctxt "mn12:29.4"
msgid "imā kho, sāriputta, aṭṭha parisā."
msgstr "These are the eight assemblies."

msgctxt "mn12:29.5"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, sāriputta, catūhi vesārajjehi samannāgato tathāgato imā aṭṭha "
"parisā upasaṅkamati ajjhogāhati."
msgstr ""
"Possessing these four kinds of self-assurance, the Realized One approaches "
"and enters right into these eight assemblies."

# BB has “many hundreds of assemblies” but at AN 8.69 he changes it to “an assembly consisting of many hundreds”
msgctxt "mn12:29.6"
msgid ""
"Abhijānāmi kho panāhaṃ, sāriputta, anekasataṃ khattiyaparisaṃ upasaṅkamitā."
msgstr "I recall having approached an assembly of hundreds of aristocrats."

msgctxt "mn12:29.7"
msgid ""
"Tatrapi mayā sannisinnapubbañceva, sallapitapubbañca, sākacchā ca "
"samāpajjitapubbā."
msgstr "There I used to sit with them, converse, and engage in discussion."

msgctxt "mn12:29.8"
msgid ""
"Tatra vata maṃ bhayaṃ vā sārajjaṃ vā okkamissatīti nimittametaṃ, sāriputta, "
"na samanupassāmi."
msgstr "But I don’t see any reason to feel afraid or insecure."

msgctxt "mn12:29.9"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, sāriputta, nimittaṃ asamanupassanto khemappatto abhayappatto "
"vesārajjappatto viharāmi."
msgstr "Since I see no such reason, I live secure, fearless, and assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya30"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.73"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc30"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:30.1"
msgid "Abhijānāmi kho panāhaṃ, sāriputta, anekasataṃ brāhmaṇaparisaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "I recall having approached an assembly of hundreds of brahmins …"

msgctxt "mn12:30.2"
msgid "gahapatiparisaṃ …"
msgstr "householders …"

msgctxt "mn12:30.3"
msgid "samaṇaparisaṃ …"
msgstr "ascetics …"

msgctxt "mn12:30.4"
msgid "cātumahārājikaparisaṃ …"
msgstr "the gods under the Four Great Kings …"

msgctxt "mn12:30.5"
msgid "tāvatiṃsaparisaṃ …"
msgstr "the gods under the Thirty-Three …"

msgctxt "mn12:30.6"
msgid "māraparisaṃ …"
msgstr "Māras …"

msgctxt "mn12:30.7"
msgid "brahmaparisaṃ upasaṅkamitā."
msgstr "Brahmās."

msgctxt "mn12:30.8"
msgid ""
"Tatrapi mayā sannisinnapubbañceva, sallapitapubbañca, sākacchā ca "
"samāpajjitapubbā."
msgstr "There too I used to sit with them, converse, and engage in discussion."

