#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya56"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc54"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:56.1"
msgid ""
"Tāyapi kho ahaṃ, sāriputta, iriyāya tāya paṭipadāya tāya dukkarakārikāya "
"nājjhagamaṃ uttariṃ manussadhammā alamariyañāṇadassanavisesaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But Sāriputta, I did not achieve any superhuman distinction in knowledge and "
"vision worthy of the noble ones by that conduct, that practice, that "
"grueling work."

msgctxt "mn12:56.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn12:56.3"
msgid ""
"Imissāyeva ariyāya paññāya anadhigamā, yāyaṃ ariyā paññā adhigatā ariyā "
"niyyānikā, niyyāti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāya."
msgstr ""
"Because I didn’t achieve that noble wisdom that’s noble and emancipating, "
"and which leads someone who practices it to the complete ending of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya57"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.82"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc55"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:57.1"
msgid "Santi kho pana, sāriputta, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "mn12:57.2"
msgid "‘saṃsārena suddhī’ti."
msgstr "‘Purity comes from transmigration.’"

#. VAR: Na kho pana so → na kho paneso (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "mn12:57.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho pana so, sāriputta, saṃsāro sulabharūpo yo mayā asaṃsaritapubbo iminā "
"dīghena addhunā, aññatra suddhāvāsehi devehi."
msgstr ""
"But it’s not easy to find a realm that I haven’t previously transmigrated to "
"in all this long time, except for the gods of the pure abodes."

msgctxt "mn12:57.4"
msgid ""
"Suddhāvāse cāhaṃ, sāriputta, deve saṃsareyyaṃ, nayimaṃ lokaṃ "
"punarāgaccheyyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"For if I had transmigrated to the gods of the pure abodes I would not have "
"returned to this realm again."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya58"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc56"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:58.1"
msgid "Santi kho pana, sāriputta, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "mn12:58.2"
msgid "‘upapattiyā suddhī’ti."
msgstr "‘Purity comes from rebirth.’"

msgctxt "mn12:58.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho pana sā, sāriputta, upapatti sulabharūpā yā mayā anupapannapubbā "
"iminā dīghena addhunā, aññatra suddhāvāsehi devehi."
msgstr ""
"But it’s not easy to find any rebirth that I haven’t previously been reborn "
"in …"

msgctxt "mn12:58.4"
msgid ""
"Suddhāvāse cāhaṃ, sāriputta, deve upapajjeyyaṃ, nayimaṃ lokaṃ "
"punarāgaccheyyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya59"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc57"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:59.1"
msgid "Santi kho pana, sāriputta, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "mn12:59.2"
msgid "‘āvāsena suddhī’ti."
msgstr "‘Purity comes from abode of rebirth.’"

#. VAR: anāvuṭṭhapubbo → anāvutthapubbo (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "mn12:59.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho pana so, sāriputta, āvāso sulabharūpo yo mayā anāvuṭṭhapubbo iminā "
"dīghena addhunā, aññatra suddhāvāsehi devehi."
msgstr "But it’s not easy to find an abode where I haven’t previously abided …"

msgctxt "mn12:59.4"
msgid ""
"Suddhāvāse cāhaṃ, sāriputta, deve āvaseyyaṃ, nayimaṃ lokaṃ punarāgaccheyyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya60"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc58"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:60.1"
msgid "Santi kho pana, sāriputta, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "mn12:60.2"
msgid "‘yaññena suddhī’ti."
msgstr "‘Purity comes from sacrifice.’"

msgctxt "mn12:60.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho pana so, sāriputta, yañño sulabharūpo yo mayā ayiṭṭhapubbo iminā "
"dīghena addhunā, tañca kho raññā vā satā khattiyena muddhāvasittena "
"brāhmaṇena vā mahāsālena."
msgstr ""
"But it’s not easy to find a sacrifice that I haven’t previously offered in "
"all this long time, when I was an anointed king or a well-to-do brahmin."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya61"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc59"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:61.1"
msgid "Santi kho pana, sāriputta, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "mn12:61.2"
msgid "‘aggiparicariyāya suddhī’ti."
msgstr "‘Purity comes from serving the sacred flame.’"

msgctxt "mn12:61.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho pana so, sāriputta, aggi sulabharūpo yo mayā apariciṇṇapubbo iminā "
"dīghena addhunā, tañca kho raññā vā satā khattiyena muddhāvasittena "
"brāhmaṇena vā mahāsālena."
msgstr ""
"But it’s not easy to find a fire that I haven’t previously served in all "
"this long time, when I was an anointed king or a well-to-do brahmin."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya62"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.83"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc60"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:62.1"
msgid "Santi kho pana, sāriputta, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "mn12:62.2"
msgid ""
"‘yāvadevāyaṃ bhavaṃ puriso daharo hoti yuvā susukāḷakeso bhadrena yobbanena "
"samannāgato paṭhamena vayasā tāvadeva paramena paññāveyyattiyena samannāgato "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"‘So long as this gentleman is youthful, young, black-haired, blessed with "
"youth, in the prime of life he will be endowed with perfect proficiency in "
"wisdom."

msgctxt "mn12:62.3"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho ayaṃ bhavaṃ puriso jiṇṇo hoti vuddho mahallako addhagato "
"vayoanuppatto, āsītiko vā nāvutiko vā vassasatiko vā jātiyā, atha tamhā "
"paññāveyyattiyā, parihāyatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"But when he’s old, elderly, and senior, advanced in years, and has reached "
"the final stage of life—eighty, ninety, or a hundred years old—he will lose "
"his proficiency in wisdom.’"

msgctxt "mn12:62.4"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, sāriputta, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

msgctxt "mn12:62.5"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ kho pana, sāriputta, etarahi jiṇṇo vuddho mahallako addhagato "
"vayoanuppatto, āsītiko me vayo vattati."
msgstr ""
"For now I am old, elderly, and senior, I’m advanced in years, and have "
"reached the final stage of life. I am eighty years old."

msgctxt "mn12:62.6"
msgid ""
"Idha me assu, sāriputta, cattāro sāvakā vassasatāyukā vassasatajīvino, "
"paramāya satiyā ca gatiyā ca dhitiyā ca samannāgatā paramena ca "
"paññāveyyattiyena."
msgstr ""
"Suppose I had four disciples with a lifespan of a hundred years. And they "
"each were perfect in memory, range, retention, and perfect proficiency in "
"wisdom."

#. VAR: daḷhadhammā → daḷhadhammo (sabbattha)
msgctxt "mn12:62.7"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, sāriputta, daḷhadhammā dhanuggaho sikkhito katahattho katūpāsano "
"lahukena asanena appakasireneva tiriyaṃ tālacchāyaṃ atipāteyya, "
msgstr ""
"Imagine how easily a well-trained expert archer with a strong bow would "
"shoot a light arrow across the shadow of a palm tree. "

msgctxt "mn12:62.8"
msgid ""
"evaṃ adhimattasatimanto evaṃ adhimattagatimanto evaṃ adhimattadhitimanto "
"evaṃ paramena paññāveyyattiyena samannāgatā."
msgstr ""
"That’s how extraordinary they were in memory, range, retention, and perfect "
"proficiency in wisdom."

msgctxt "mn12:62.9"
msgid ""
"Te maṃ catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ upādāyupādāya pañhaṃ puccheyyuṃ, puṭṭho "
"puṭṭho cāhaṃ tesaṃ byākareyyaṃ, byākatañca me byākatato dhāreyyuṃ, na ca maṃ "
"dutiyakaṃ uttari paṭipuccheyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
"They’d bring up questions about the four kinds of mindfulness meditation "
"again and again, and I would answer each question. They’d remember the "
"answers and not ask the same question twice."

msgctxt "mn12:62.10"
msgid ""
"Aññatra asitapītakhāyitasāyitā aññatra uccārapassāvakammā, aññatra "
"niddākilamathapaṭivinodanā apariyādinnāyevassa, sāriputta, tathāgatassa "
"dhammadesanā, apariyādinnaṃyevassa tathāgatassa dhammapadabyañjanaṃ, "
"apariyādinnaṃyevassa tathāgatassa pañhapaṭibhānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And they’d pause only to eat and drink, go to the toilet, and sleep to "
"dispel weariness. But the Realized One would not run out of Dhamma "
"teachings, words and phrases of the teachings, or spontaneous answers."

msgctxt "mn12:62.11"
msgid ""
"Atha me te cattāro sāvakā vassasatāyukā vassasatajīvino vassasatassa "
"accayena kālaṃ kareyyuṃ."
msgstr "And at the end of a hundred years my four disciples would pass away."

msgctxt "mn12:62.12"
msgid ""
"Mañcakena cepi maṃ, sāriputta, pariharissatha, nevatthi tathāgatassa "
"paññāveyyattiyassa aññathattaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Even if you have to carry me around on a stretcher, there will never be any "
"deterioration in the Realized One’s proficiency in wisdom."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya63"></a>
#. VAR: Yaṃ kho taṃ → yaṃ kho panetaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "mn12:63.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kho taṃ, sāriputta, sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr "And if there’s anyone of whom it may be rightly said that"

msgctxt "mn12:63.2"
msgid ""
"‘asammohadhammo satto loke uppanno bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya "
"lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan’ti, mameva taṃ sammā "
"vadamāno vadeyya "
msgstr ""
"a being not liable to delusion has arisen in the world for the welfare and "
"happiness of the people, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods and "
"humans, it’s of me that this should be said.”"

msgctxt "mn12:63.3"
msgid ""
"‘asammohadhammo satto loke uppanno bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya "
"lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya64"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc61"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:64.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā nāgasamālo bhagavato piṭṭhito ṭhito hoti "
"bhagavantaṃ bījayamāno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Nāgasamāla was standing behind the Buddha fanning "
"him."

msgctxt "mn12:64.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā nāgasamālo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then he said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "mn12:64.3"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing!"

msgctxt "mn12:64.4"
msgid "Api hi me, bhante, imaṃ dhammapariyāyaṃ sutvā lomāni haṭṭhāni."
msgstr ""
"While I was listening to this exposition of the teaching my hair stood up!"

msgctxt "mn12:64.5"
msgid "Konāmo ayaṃ, bhante, dhammapariyāyo”ti?"
msgstr "What is the name of this exposition of the teaching?”"

msgctxt "mn12:64.6"
msgid ""
"“Tasmātiha tvaṃ, nāgasamāla, imaṃ dhammapariyāyaṃ lomahaṃsanapariyāyotveva "
"naṃ dhārehī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Well, Nāgasamāla, you may remember this exposition of the teaching as ‘The "
"Hair-raising Discourse’.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc62"></a>
msgctxt "mn12:64.7"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn12:64.8"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā nāgasamālo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Nāgasamāla was happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn12:64.9"
msgid "Mahāsīhanādasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
